Tips for increasing engagement
1. Record in different Angles
 - When you record in different angles it keeps your audience attention because it’s not slow and there is so much going on that it keeps everyone interested . You want content that will keep the views coming back and make sure that it is memorable content as well.

2. Create Reel under 10 seconds
 - Did you know that the average attention span is up to 8 seconds only?
 - This means that people will be less likely to watch your Instagram reels if they’re longer than 8-10 seconds. They may be too busy scrolling to the next reel if you couldn’t get their attention in the first few seconds.
 - Sure, you can engage them from the start by telling an intriguing story, sharing an interesting fact or stimulating their curiosity.
3. Create Valuable content for your audience
 -  It’s no secret that Reels are capable of catapulting a brand’s reach and impressions. But the ones that stand out are the videos that provide real value. 
 - The secret? Knowing who you’re speaking to and what their expectations are. 
 - Whether your looking for a quick tip , dinner spots in a area near you or even a recipe to try out to make for a special night or just for yourself.

The Secret to having a Glow. Step 1-5: Everyday I make sure to take care of my skin. 
Step 1 to clear skin : Use a cleanser. Doesn’t have to be just for your face but you can use a good cleanser for your whole body to get rid of any dirt. But when you are drying your face make sure to pat and not rub so the fabric from rubbing your face will not harm your skin. Step 2 : Use a Toner. Toners are initially marketed to remove any leftover traces of cleanser and tighten the skin but it can also serve as a delivery system for antioxidants, and even toning acids. 
Step 3: Moisturize . You always want to keep your skin moisturized and hydrated. 
Step 4: Use Sunscreen ALWAYS ALWAYS ALWAYS! My favorite sunscreen is @supergoop ‘s Unseen Sunscreen and now they have Unscreen Sunscreen Body, which is a life saver since I love to go for a hike and be outdoors. Supergoop! Unseen Sunscreen is so much better than other sunscreens because it’s clear and you can hardly see it - but it works! 
Step 5: Always use a good sunscreen with full spectrum SPF that protects against UV, especially for this spring and summer season. #ad
